		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Managed to pick this one up quite.quickly Scott. If you change the emphasis on the descending tenths it sounds a bit like that muted trumpet chromatic motif in Thunderbirds to indicate a fail &#8211; wah wah waaaaaaaaah it went &#8211; perhaps a bit before your time! ;-)</p>
